snippet.textDisplay:
Everyone: Hey, give us ahsoka.
EA: So here we have ewoks and an imperial arc trooper!

Seriously now. You guys have improved this game A LOT since it came out, but it took you 3 YEARS to add content that should have been there from the start! You are adding Scariff only now, I hope you'll give us Jyn as a hero too right? Cause there are close to zero good female heroes in this game, eventhough star wars have quite a number of good ones.

You did good with the clone wars phase, but it still feels like it's missing content. It would be great if we could play on different maps with different eras, such as galactic civil war on felucia and clone wars on mos eisley, that alone would improve so much the lack of maps the game has. Also, someone mentioned here already, it would be nice to have chat commands like battlefield to coordinate with your team! There should be a simple conquest mode, just like the old battlefront, for every map and era, not just the clone wars capital ship assault, because that was THE core of the game after all.

I think the game has improved a lot, it is even more playable then it was at the beginning, with this broken level up cards system. but it still proves broken a lot of times, and some of the skins feel so lazy! I mean, there are 2 damaged grievous but none of them has that goddamn badass cape! Why?? You can have dooku on pijamas and yoda with a stupid hood but not Darth vader with a broken mask or something, or even boba fett with his father's armour, darth maul with his prosthetic legs, Luke with a jedi cape, Old han and luke, anakin and obi wan from episode II... I understand that it isn't very easy to make realistic models, but I think the priorities here are messed up.

You are adding Scariff only now, I hope you'll give us Jyn as a hero too right? Cause there are close to zero good female heroes in this game, eventhough star wars have quite a number of good ones.

You did good with the clone wars phase, but it still feels like it's missing content. It would be great if we could play on different maps with different eras, such as galactic civil war on felucia and clone wars on mos eisley, that alone would improve so much the lack of maps the game has. Also, someone mentioned here already, it would be nice to have chat commands like battlefield to coordinate with your team! There should be a simple conquest mode, just like the old battlefront, for every map and era, not just the clone wars capital ship assault, because that was THE core of the game after all.

I think the game has improved a lot, it is even more playable then it was at the beginning, with this broken level up cards system. but it still proves broken a lot of times, and some of the skins feel so lazy! I mean, there are 2 damaged grievous but none of them has that goddamn badass cape! Why?? You can have dooku on pijamas and yoda with a stupid hood but not Darth vader with a broken mask or something, or even boba fett with his father's armour, darth maul with his prosthetic legs, Luke with a jedi cape, Old han and luke,  anakin and obi wan from episode II... I understand that it isn't very easy to make realistic models, but I think the priorities here are messed up.
